  "detailed_description": "You'll be at the heart of all the action, collaborating with your team to develop tactics and take down enemies. Conquer rival teams on different maps, shaping the game's flow with your weapon choices and movement style. Showcase your skills by competing against other players in the competitive arena or join team-based modes to strategize with your squad. The wide array of weapons in the game allows you to customize and shape your gameplay according to your style. If you're the best player, it's time to make your name known in this competitive world!<br><br><br>  <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes:</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Capture The Flag</h2><br> -Capture and defend the opponent's flag<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Conguest</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2550440/extras/49957f4d02c9bdd42f45051c6307e571.poster.avif?t=1698690380\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2550440/extras/49957f4d02c9bdd42f45051c6307e571.webm?t=1698690380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2550440/extras/49957f4d02c9bdd42f45051c6307e571.mp4?t=1698690380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-Classic conquering mechanics, the one with the most territories wins the game                               <br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DeathMatch</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2550440/extras/919ca234a0422570080f8b747a18706e.poster.avif?t=1698690380\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2550440/extras/919ca234a0422570080f8b747a18706e.webm?t=1698690380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.a